libs.content:
find_library(obs_library
    names
    obs
    "obs studio"
    hints
    "${obs_library_search_dir}"
    paths
    "${obs_root_dir}"
    path_suffixes
    "${_libsuffixes}"
)

find_library(cef_library
    "chromium embedded framework"
    names
    cef
    libcef
    paths
    ${cef_root_dir}
    ${cef_root_dir}
    path_suffixes
    /release
)

find_library(cef_library_debug
    "chromium embedded framework"
    names
    cef
    libcef
    paths
    ${cef_root_dir}
    ${cef_root_dir}
    path_suffixes
    /debug
)

find_library(cefwrapper_library
    "cef wrapper"
    names
    cef_dll_wrapper
    libcef_dll_wrapper
    paths
    ${cef_root_dir}
    ${cef_root_dir}/libcef_dll
    ${cef_root_dir}/libcef_dll_wrapper
    ${cef_root_dir}/build/libcef_dll
    ${cef_root_dir}/build/libcef_dll_wrapper
    path_suffixes
    /release
)

find_library(cefwrapper_library_debug
    "cef wrapper"
    names
    cef_dll_wrapper
    libcef_dll_wrapper
    paths
    ${cef_root_dir}/libcef_dll/debug
    ${cef_root_dir}/libcef_dll_wrapper/debug
    ${cef_root_dir}/build/libcef_dll/debug
    ${cef_root_dir}/build/libcef_dll_wrapper/debug
)
